binary.description:
During your training, you found a fellow spaceman-in-training. Hiding in a dark corner, he seem to be alive yet aloof. Hugging his knee close to the chest with his head tuck down, he mumbled "find the password... find the pass.. find th pass.. fithpass.."

Author: Bing Zhong
binary.name: FreeBie

binary.description:
A few meters away from the man, you spotted a large note. It says "Free us! Quit when you're done! FREE US!"

Author: Eugene Tan
binary.name: FreeUs

binary.description:
Hoping to get a clearer look on his face, you approach the man and tap his shoulder. He shot up and burst into screams! "FILTHY PASSON!, DONT YOU TOUCH ME!!!" He shove you back to the ground and slowly sat down with his legs to his chest. As he slowly tuck his head, he mumbered "find the password.."

Author: Ng Bing Zhong
binary.name: FreeMe

cryptography.description:
Apart from reaching the planet, populating the planet under our Motherland's flag is equally important. Your crew must lead 100 colonists to establish your state's foothold before all others. Coordinates are given to you locked by an SSH key. Hmm.. what to do? whaaat toooo doooooo :)

Author: Ng Bing Zhong

Alternate Host: keeper@52.221.216.127:5002
cryptography.name: Study space colonisation

cryptography.description:
Your crew will be subjected to an endurance test to ensure you can survive the 1,400 light year trip via a 88-hour simulated flight. No one can intense such a long simulation without food and water. Yet, a SSH private key is given to you. If only you can decipher the message that is encrypted in DES and input the safe word. Pineapple juice? 🍍

Message:
5ed0b9428aa782f5830fcbaf2731c7d95aeca05cd0ad789e282806d86d02c362abe4ed3d98b6ad39

Author: Ng Bing Zhong
cryptography.name: Long duration flight test

feedback.description: Thanks for completing Major 1! We would love your feedback.
feedback.name: Cyber League Feedback

forensics.description:
To root out spies, an encrypted PCAP file is given to each team. It is encrypted with the motherland's key. Only a true soldier will know! Are you the spy?!

Author: Yong Wen
forensics.name: Conduct endurance training

forensics.description:
One of our fellow operators has sent a secret transmission. We managed to get 70% of the message, I wonder if you can figure out the rest.

Author: Hades95200
forensics.name: Simulated space combat

forensics.description:
A file has been leaked out from the higher-ups, and it is rumored to contain chairman mao's little red book, which is the space politics bible that we will ever need.

Author: Wan Qing
forensics.name: Understand space politics

forensics.description:
Each team is given a file to mess with. Fix it within the time limit and prove your worth to the motherland!

Author: Yong Wen
forensics.name: Physical and Mental test

miscellaneous.description:
Say goodbye (or good riddance) to everyone you know and love. 

Note: Compatible with all galaxy devices.

Author: Hakkasuru
miscellaneous.name: Write farewell letters

mobile.description:
As a soldier from the Motherland, being captured only makes you a laughing stock. This will train you to capture enemies, and guide you on how your hostages should be treated according to the law of the Motherland. All enemies are equipped with a bodycam APK. You will learn to decompile and locate sensitive information. "I spy with my little eye".

Author: Wang Qing
mobile.name: Prisoner of war training

reverse engineering.description:
The recognised imaginary boundary of space is about 99.8km. A calculator application is used to transmit a confidential message. A secret code is used to decrypt the message, let's see if you can find it.

Author: Joshua Wee Wei En
reverse engineering.name: Conduct parachuting from high altitude

smart contract.description:
The funds are lost somewhere on this platform. Find the missing funds from draftdown labs. We need it to fund our mission. Use our script to validate the transaction.

> Note: No brute force or fuzzing is needed for the search! Just use your eyes.

>Use CYBERLEAGUE{} flag format

Author: Draftdown Labs
smart contract.name: Space Contract

steganography.description:
Imposters!!! Two identical images were transmitted hoisting our motherland's flag. There can only be one vessel with our glorious flag! Determine the imposter, shoot at sight!

Author: Yong Wen
steganography.name: Simulated abandon vessel

A new HTML station is in progress to process your fuel. Due to the ongoing war between cossacks and baltic hoomans, some HTML sub stations are inaccessible. For sake of clarity, some warnings signs has been set up as well. Dont try to snoop pass that! 

Author: Aizuddin

web.description:
You know what's worse than a bomb? FAILURE TO CONTAIN ONE! You're going to contain and eliminate any bomb, explosive or the tiniest spark in under a minute.

Author: Hades95200

CHECK OUT /defuse

web.description:
Halfway through the journey, your team received a distress call from a friendly lunar base codenamed "SEETF". You dispatched a taskforce in a pigeon aircraft to further investigate the cause.

Flag is admin's launch code.

Author: zeyu2001 @ SEE
web.name: Pigeon Aircraft Takeoff

web.description:
Sit tight, put on your seat belt... and test our API system. Seriously? What were you expecting?

Author: Hades95200
